524xh;0.111xw,0.459xh&resize=640:*", "card": "summary_large_image"}, "auto-publish": "timely", "sailthru.excerpt": "<p class=\"dropcap\">Every fall and winter, an endearing shoe style pops up and prevails above the rest\u2014whether it\u2019s a statement mule in early autumn, a satin <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40315714/best-ballet-flats/\" target=\"_blank\">ballet flat</a> toward the end of summer, or a <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g44938539/most-comfortable-loafers-women/\" target=\"_blank\">comfortable loafer</a> that transcends every season and weather transition. This season, however, we\u2019re looking toward a reworked classic and nominating the best sock boots as the essential winter shoe. Take <a href=\"https://nomasei.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nomasei</a>\u2019s offerings, for example: Season after season, the label\u2019s Strada and Aria sock boots are some of street style\u2019s favorites for a modern and unique look, regardless of the runway\u2019s dominant <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/a44751678/fall-2023-shoe-trends/\" target=\"_blank\">shoe trends</a>.</p><p>At this point, with the range of structured <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40746010/best-leather-boots-women/\" target=\"_blank\">leather boots</a> on the market, a sock boot seems almost irregular. Still, Nomasei co-founder Marine Braquet  thinks the sock boot will endure. \u201cThe trend keeps coming back because it flatters the silhouette, so women never get fed up,\u201d she explains. \u201cOur clients often say, \u2018It\u2019s sexy but easy to wear!\u2019 and it is\u2014chic, and extremely comfortable when well made. All of our sock boots are timeless, so it\u2019s a safe bet.\u201d</p><p>Safe bet it is\u2014modern twists on the sock boot work with virtually everything, from knitted maxi skirts and baggy denim to oversize <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g37898395/womens-suit-sets/\" target=\"_blank\">suiting</a> and jersey midi dresses (and they\u2019re one of the <a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g45303126/most-comfortable-boots-for-women/\" target=\"_blank\">most comfortable boot</a> styles around). The best sock boots for women are as walkable as they are sleek. With styles ranging from extra-sharp pointed toes to knee boots that stretch comfortably over the leg, shop our favorite versions of the season ahead.</p><p>[product-summary-view headline='The Best Sock Boots for Women in 2024' showHeadline='true'][/product-summary-view]</p>", "sailthru.tags": "fashion,Fashion,trends,Trends & Shopping Guides,the-edit-fashion,The Edit: Fashion,Harper's BAZAAR-US", "sailthru.date": "2023-12-04 16:45:00", "sailthru.socialtitle": "Spend All Winter in These 15 Sock Boots", "sailthru.contenttype": "listicle"}, "movies": [], "publish_date": 1701708300.0, "source": "https://www.harpersbazaar.com", "summary": ""}